      "para_id": "Q001750.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad : Ur-Nanibgal , governor of Nibru , child of Lugal-engardug , governor of Nibru , is your servant ."
    }
